 Create Venv ------
WINDOWS:   py/python -m venv venv
MacOS:     python3 -m venv venv

------ Activate venv ------
WIN:   venv\Scripts\activate
MacOSs: source venv/bin/activate

------ Install Flask ------
pip install Flask

------ Run server.py file ------
WIN:   py/python server.py
MacOS: python3 server.py




